data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Welcome to our Standard Room at Imperial Hotel! Nestled in vibrant Durban, our cozy rooms offer a relaxing retreat after a day of exploration. Choose between queen-sized or twin beds, accommodating up to two adults and one child comfortably. Refresh in your private bathroom with a convenient shower/tub combination and find all the essentials for a pleasant stay, including complimentary Wi-Fi and a flat-screen TV. Embrace comfort and convenience during your visit to Imperial Hotel!
